ZH: 我们终将成功的。
EN: We will eventually succeed.

ZH: 时间终将证明一切。
EN: Time will eventually prove everything.

ZH: 我们终将变老。
EN: We will eventually grow old.

ZH: 他终将明白真相。
EN: He will eventually understand the truth.

ZH: 终将有一天，你会感激我。
EN: One day you will eventually thank me.

ZH: 她终将学会宽容。
EN: She will eventually learn to be tolerant.

ZH: 终将会有一个好的结局。
EN: There will eventually be a good ending.

ZH: 终将到来的春天会带来希望。
EN: The coming spring will eventually bring hope.

ZH: 他终将回到家乡。
EN: He will eventually return to his hometown.

ZH: 终将会有解决方案的。
EN: There will eventually be a solution.

ZH: 他们终将相聚一堂。
EN: They will eventually reunite.

ZH: 终将逝去的岁月不能回头。
EN: The passed years will eventually not come back.

ZH: 她终将体会到健康的重要性。
EN: She will eventually realize the importance of health.

ZH: 终将有人懂得你的良苦用心。
EN: Eventually someone will understand your good intentions.

ZH: 他们终将面对现实。
EN: They will eventually face reality.

ZH: 终将迎来成功的那一天。
EN: The day of success will eventually come.

ZH: 他终将成为一位伟大的领袖。
EN: He will eventually become a great leader.

ZH: 终将明白这段经历的意义。
EN: Eventually, the meaning of this experience will be understood.

ZH: 我们终将找到解决办法。
EN: We will eventually find a solution.

ZH: 挫折终将成为成功的垫脚石。
EN: Setbacks will eventually become stepping stones to success.
